Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The World Is Shaken!\NThe Ruler's Judgment and the Five Elders' Actions!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While the murder of King Cobra\Nwas kept hidden,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the curtain came down on the Reverie.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He must still be around! Let's catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,King Cobra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...cannot collapse here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I must tell Luffy and Princess Vivi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...King Cobra's words!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you found them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra-{\i1}sama{\i} hasn't returned\Nfrom his meeting with the Five Elders...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have no idea where Vivi-{\i1}sama{\i} went.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on in Mary Geoise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about\NCobra-{\i1}sama{\i}'s condition, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll search the castle one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'll look for Vivi-{\i1}sama{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Pell, search from the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Vivi-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see King Cobra!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We were told not to allow anyone in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Our king is sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anyone seen Princess Vivi of\Nthe Kingdom of Alabasta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Princess Vivi! Have you seen her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Vivi-{\i1}sama{\i}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,King Seki, Princess Comane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to escort you to the ship\Nat the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hide!\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! It's just a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Be more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask you to come with me,\Nso don't tell me what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,These ones next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a royal family's baggage.\NTreat it with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Wapol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hide in those boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good idea, isn't it? Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll find us! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for escorting them.\NThe Navy will take over from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,King Tea IV is on board now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up with bringing in the luggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We managed to sneak in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safe for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But what should I do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to tell the world\Nwhat happened at the Reverie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that,\Nthe Government will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I turn you over\Nto Navy soldiers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But just like me,\Nyou don't want to be found, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's right...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since I witnessed the dark side of\Nthe Government...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do these things keep happening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! I'm sure he won't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I have the type of story\Nthat he craves...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A Transponder Snail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you had it! Can I borrow it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cheapskate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my lifeline!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mor-{\i}chan{\i1}! It's me, Wapol!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How was the Reverie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not important!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet something happened to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't talk about it over the Snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll kill me if they find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I want you to harbor me\Nin exchange for my story!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What country's ship is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eigis Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay. We'll approach the ship\Npretending to be researching a story.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Use that chance to get aboard ours.\NDon't let anyone see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,News so big\Nthat a king's life is threatened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So what exactly did you see, Wapol?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the last person\NI want to tell about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go back to your people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It was CP-0 who captured me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I meet up with my people,\Nthey'll take me again by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So let me use your Transponder Snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to call my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the last thing you should do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Let me just use it for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:18.78,On Top,,0,0,0,,SHIP OF THE TAJINE KINGDOM\N(SHIP'S HOLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm hungry...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:25.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,SHIP OF THE KINGDOM OF LULUSIA\N(SHIP BOTTOM)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once I get to Lulusia,\Neverything'll be alright...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Sabo-{\i1}kun{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Live on!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vivi, Wapol...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and a few other stowaways\Nlurked on the ships...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that were taking various monarchs\Nback to their homes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It didn't take long before the murder of Cobra,\NKing of the Kingdom of Alabasta,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:11:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the disappearance of Princess Vivi\Nbecame known worldwide.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,HOLY LAND MARY GEOISE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo is another man with a strange fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is surrounded by "D"\Nmore than he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to put an end\Nto that Egghead matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Imu-{\i1}sama{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:26.89,On Top,,0,0,0,,CHAMBER OF FLOWERS INSIDE PANGAEA CASTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to use the Mother Flame\Nthat Vegapunk invented.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if we don't try it,\Nwe'll never know if that thing is real or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's figure out what to do with Egghead\Nbased on the results of that experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The testing site should be in areas with forests\Nrather than at sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kingdom of Lulusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a lot of people live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't matter.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The world should be\Nas the Creators want it to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you choose Lulusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're right...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make the necessary preparations.\NWe request your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In Lulusia,\Nthere are signs of revolt among the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This will serve as a good lesson\Nfor everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually,\Nwhen we have that power at our disposal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The long battle will come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Vivi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:59.86,On Top,,0,0,0,,ST. JAYGARCIA SATURN\NGODHEAD OF SCIENCE & DEFENSE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,ST. MARCUS MARS\NGODHEAD OF ENVIRONMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:03.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,ST. TOPMAN WARCURY\NGODHEAD OF JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,ST. ETHANBARON V. NUSJURO\NGODHEAD OF FINANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:07.37,On Top,,0,0,0,,ST. SHEPHERD JU PETER\NGODHEAD OF AGRICULTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:31.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,NAVY HEADQUARTERS, NEW WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A report for Fleet Admiral Sakazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There are revolts in the Tajine Kingdom\Nand the Eigis Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just crush every last one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Load ammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Deploy all the Seraphim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:14:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! We'll launch the Seraphim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Navy was extremely busy\Nwith the abolition of the Seven Warlords system{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the uprisings\Nin various affiliated countries.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However,\Nthis was also the start of the new Navy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Nthere's been one revolt after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodile showed up\Non the Emptee Bluffs Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sables!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:38.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,KAMABAKKA QUEENDOM\NPEACHY ISLAND, GRAND LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as we arrived at the Kingdom of Lulusia,\NKing Seki and Princess Comane got captured...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...by the people who were waiting for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and just get me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a stowaway, but they welcomed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's because\Nyou were their best hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I saw the newspaper article\Nfor the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:15.24,On Top,,0,0,0,,KING COBRA ASSASSINATED
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and learned that I was framed\Nfor the King's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Unsurprisingly, people considered me a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but I held my tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I felt their growing thirst\Nfor revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the influence of Betty and others,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,there were many people in Lulusia\Nwho wanted to join the Revolutionary Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're the ones I brought here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do, you pieces of trash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get killed or fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose your own destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our Betty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I couldn't get\Nan Encryption Transponder Snail in Lulusia,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so I wasn't able to call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I made an indirect call\Nas soon as we sailed out, and that was the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:08.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,KAMABAKKA QUEENDOM\NKINGDOM OF LULUSIA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dragon-{\i}san{\i1}!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,King Cobra's assassin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...isn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the Government eavesdropped on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:24.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,KINGDOM OF LULUSIA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and thought I was in Lulusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But in reality,\NI was already out at sea with the enlistees.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You were on the call\Nwhen it happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The destruction of the Kingdom of Lulusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There was panic on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So many people left their families behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They saw their home island\Nblown away in front of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That must have been tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A large shadow covered the sky above...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And the next moment, it was already...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A large shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be anything biological or natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Something really dark\Nwas flying over the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Sabo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you mentioned Imu earlier, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This may sound rather bizarre to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but among the First Twenty\Nwho created this world 800 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a king named Saint Imu\Nfrom the Nerona Dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We know there is an ability\Nto make someone immortal in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But this means that\Nsomeone has actually used it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's proof that there's a person out there\Nwho doesn't know death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that's the person I saw?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's just a coincidence\Nthat they have the same name...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But who else would the Five Elders\Nhumble themselves to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the highest authority\Namong the Celestial Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...who flatter themselves\Nto be descendants of gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,One more surprising thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If the thing that you saw destroying the country\Nfrom the clouds was a Government weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,only Vegapunk could have made such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Iva.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk wouldn't make such a blatant tool\Nfor killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if it was an Ancient Weapon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If Imu is an ancient, living person,\Nit makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin confirmed the existence of\Nthe Ancient Weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But if they had it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,why didn't they use it until now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And why use it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Present day.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Celestial Dragon has just been executed\Nin the Holy Land Mary Geoise today.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However,\Nit will never be reported to the world.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good riddance-{\i1}eh{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he sided with them, fools in the lower world\Nhave been pushing their luck recently-{\i1}eh{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all his fault\Nthat we lost our food supply-{\i1}eh{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The judge was a man who was once active\Nas a champion on an island called God Valley.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is now the Supreme Commander of\Nthe Holy Knights.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}St. Figarland Garling.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one executed...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...was the man who defended the Fish-Men.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}St. Donquixote Myosgard.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who defends scum\Nis lower than scum they protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:21.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doredake hashitte kita noka{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:28.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wakaranai mama kizuato kazoeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:35.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zutto atama no naka ni aru takara no chizu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:42.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mirai wo sagashi tsuzuketeru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:49.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hontou no yakusoku wa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real promise{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:56.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mune no oku no motto oku ni aru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:21:05.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dare mo mina oitsukenai yume{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:21:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream that no one can catch up with{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:11.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitotsu dakishimete{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:18.31,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}taiyou no youni warau anata e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:25.24,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ano hi to onaji uta wo utau yo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:32.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}otona ni nattemo wasuretakunai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget even when I grow up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:39.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kono negai ga todoku made{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dive into the Sea of Information!\NThe Punk Records Library!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Lilith, one of the Satellites of\NDr. Vegapunk, the genius scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:22:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Edison, also Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll introduce this one!\NNefeltari Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the princess of the Kingdom of Alabasta\Nand Nefeltari Cobra's only daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She was born on February 2nd and\Nlikes curry, custard pudding, and mulukhiyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When she learned of the existence of Baroque Works,\Nwhich threatened the Kingdom of Alabasta,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,she infiltrated the organization herself\Nto find out who the mastermind was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She used the alias Ms. Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,After she started working with the Straw Hats,\Nshe returned to the Kingdom of Alabasta,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and together with them, she foiled\NCrocodile's plot to overthrow the kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.23,0:22:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If we ever meet again some day...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.31,0:22:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,will you call me your friend again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Vivi stayed in her beloved homeland,\Nbut her ties to the Straw Hats remain deep!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.95,0:22:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, she was kidnapped by CP-0\Nin the Holy Land Mary Geoise,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.75,0:23:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but she managed to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a little worried that she'll still be\Ntargeted by a lot of people in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen it,\Ndonate to our research fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll look back on the Navy,\Nthe perennial enemy of pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.52,0:23:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's full of tough ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.77,0:23:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to review our enemy's information.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Navy is a powerful organization.\NIt never hurts to know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Unwavering Justice! The Navy's Proud Log!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.00,0:23:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy's the future King of the Pirates!
